span.i: According to the Republic of Estonia

span.b: § 5. Results of intellectual activities to which this Act does not apply

li.span: 1) ideas, images, notions, theories, processes, systems, methods, concepts, principles, discoveries, inventions, and other results of intellectual activities which are described, explained or expressed in any other manner in a work;
3) legislation and administrative documents (acts, decrees, regulations, statutes, instructions, directives) and official translations thereof;
4) court decisions and official translations thereof;
5) official symbols of the state and insignia of organisations (flags, coats of arms, orders, medals, badges, etc.);
8) ideas and principles which underlie any element of a computer program, including those which underlie its user interfaces.

span.i: Hence it is assumed that this image has been released into the public domain. However, in some instances the use of this image might be regulated by other laws.
